A Shot at Glory;;2000;;R;;Drama,Sport;;6.3;;Michael Corrente;;Robert Duvall,Michael Keaton,Andy Gray,Finlay MacDonald,Sheila Latimer,Ally McCoist,Ida Schuster,Alex Howden,Bill Murdoch,John McVeigh,Scott Anderson,Cole Hauser,John Martin,Paul Agnew,Ian Constable,Owen Coyle,Steve Hamilton,Peter Hetherston;;Gordon McLeod is the manager of a second tier Scottish football team. Faced with pressure from his American owner, he is forced to bring on a marquee player to improve the fortunes of the team and prevents its being moved from the fiercely loyal town it's been for a century. Along the way, McLeod must battle his own demons, including long-standing tiffs with both his daughter and a former colleague who betrayed him.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0193854/